<D>__{how's he doing?}
<C>__{mrs. waters}
<D>__{he's had a tough night, hazel. his blood pressure's low. his heart }
<A>__{mrs. waters starts to cry.}
<C>__{hazel}
<D>__{what about the chemo?}
<C>__{mrs. waters}
<P>__{(shakes her head)}
<D>__{they're gonna stop the chemo.}
<A>__{they both know what that means. mrs. waters gathers herself.}
<C>__{hazel}
<D>__{can i see him?}
<C>__{mrs. waters}
<P>__{(beat)}
<D>__{we have to be a family now.}
<A>__{hazel nods. she understands.}
<C>__{mrs. waters}
<D>__{we'll tell him you were here.}
<C>__{hazel}
<D>__{if you don't mind, i will just hang for a while.}
